at these slow kinks, rather than the CIRs themselves, are more\nlikely to result in high-opacity DACs in the absorption troughs of unsaturated\nP Cygni line profiles.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Aug 1995 15:09:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-28"}
